      "span_text": "Which can be seen in Fig 5, the mass response was significantly increased from 2.15e [CITATION_1] for RP-UHPLC/MS to 1.31e 8 for HILIC-UHPLC/MS. For RP-UHPLC/MS, a wealth of information can be provided by both positive and negative modes, therefore both modes were applied in the metabonomics study (S2 Fig), while for HILIC-UHPLC/MS, more metabolite information obtained in positive mode than that in negative mode, then only positive mode was finally applied.",
